                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Do you want to develop a smaller waistline and a shredded set of abs? Then</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">,</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> you need to try the hanging leg raise.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It is designed to target the abs and engage the entire upper body, making for one incredible exercise.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Today, we will discuss how to do the hanging leg raises. We will share our expert tips, anatomy, and training recommendations to get the best results. </span></p>                    </div>
